{"tid":1721600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實手工好，磚牆都可以好實淨！","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:19.000Z","uid":105931,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97a84ecb213887cf701a4b936145e632ce4a1589","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">教學片</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1wLffrvSc8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1wLffrvSc8I&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6z%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=674d5643\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1wLffrvSc8I</a><br />\n<br />\n讀書都有教，English Bond Brickwall 其實係最實淨！詳情睇影片，其實唔難，一排橫一排正。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">示意圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i07ds9y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi07ds9y.jpg&h=dc03d106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">留意手工：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 個底一定要坐飽漿（姐係溝左英泥既水，又叫泥油！</span><br />\n<br />\n個底唔坐漿或者坐唔夠，根本咬唔實個地下，好易成幅一推就散！亦會大大增加夾車要車起會既難度！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.磚上下左右都要夠泥油！</span><br />\n<br />\n只要磚之間夠泥油，佢地既bonding會強好多，成為一幅真正既牆，比野撞時可以傳力去其他磚！而再唔係砌積木咁款一推就散！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 資源有限，唔洗砌咁高，要砌厚d!</span><br />\n<br />\n其實用黎做road block，目的係唔比車行，同埋仲要愈難清走愈有效。所以建議砌4-5磚就足夠，反而個厚度可以增加至同高度一樣！咁樣受撞時先更有力抵抗。高既牆受撞更易散既道理我諗大家都明！<br />\n<br />\n4.  有多英泥沙，可以厚厚地批埋成個面<br />\n<br />\n你批埋個面，基本上就好似一幅牆，差在未油油！要清理個陣師父同打拆無咩分別！大大增加難度！<br />\n<br />\n5. 做完泥水記得要護養<br />\n<br />\n泥水野做完一定要淋水護養，如果唔係d英泥漿好快會吸乾水而導致有裂痕。不紡係英泥開始硬時同做完後淋多兩次水<br />\n<br />\n最後，其實磚牆如果加埋插鐵，就更加可以大大力咬實兩邊，不過現場資源有限就不講了。<br />\nPs 岩岩入行幾個月，有錯請更正建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1a6b1578cdd94ac4a04f998e1c8d0e7414fa815","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:48:09.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"a3c49218f264bb72015eada6f608669d6fe76be7","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:48:32.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"90ea4cb7a41225721ca9ea49174d0b0ccf884268","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"25864211777d2f3b4a0404e71f266e392497efc4","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"73dc425829b911f4421ee45a234451b84b86b56e","tid":1721600,"uid":170335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"多謝手足貢獻<br />\n但唔鼓勵守城/陣地<br />\n磚應該落係警曱身上 又非在地上"},{"pid":"4dcc7c6a1ac40287fc2fbcf753bae13b0dae1f2d","tid":1721600,"uid":84363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe16c98900e9d01cf36a44cc4003f34a57ed9ebd","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:51:46.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"4b769d0d9ee9e5c2151b89744dcffb5d82ab2a90","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73dc425829b911f4421ee45a234451b84b86b56e","tid":1721600,"uid":170335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"多謝手足貢獻<br />\n但唔鼓勵守城/陣地<br />\n磚應該落係警曱身上 又非在地上"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"好明白你意思！但我都希望手足真係要用黎起road block 時可以更加有效咁起！當然係夠資源先啦！"},{"pid":"49dc3d71b9b7330010a06921cbbcd11d2dc8daa7","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"自推6/10"},{"pid":"113a4a556c4b0196807f5b9de835a039519c5fbf","tid":1721600,"uid":170335,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4b769d0d9ee9e5c2151b89744dcffb5d82ab2a90","tid":1721600,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":